646
01:23:35,000 --> 01:23:47,000
And, believe it or not, he's interested in going into medicine and not music as his major.

647
01:23:47,000 --> 01:23:52,000
So here we have Out of Africa, a Mozart.

648
01:23:52,000 --> 01:23:56,000
Another Albert Switzer, if you please.

