687
01:27:12,000 --> 01:27:26,000
Dr. Clemmitt's house that I first laid eyes on Elemeroseville when she spoke for the graduation of Atlanta University back in the 60s.

688
01:27:26,000 --> 01:27:39,000
And these experiences have come my way because I hung out with people who were great models.

689
01:27:39,000 --> 01:27:50,000
And who were just a terrific inspiration for me and many young people.

690
01:27:50,000 --> 01:27:57,000
And in many ways that began with your relationship with Edgar Evers.

691
01:27:57,000 --> 01:28:06,000
