01:47:48,000 --> 01:48:00,000
And when we're in risk, we're even safe. I'm black and I'm proud. I'm yellow and I'm yellow.

814
01:48:00,000 --> 01:48:10,000
I'm red, but I ain't dead. I'm brown and I'm sound. I'm white and I'm alright.

815
01:48:10,000 --> 01:48:17,000
I am gay, but I'm gotten it. I'm straight, but I'm sensible.

816
01:48:17,000 --> 01:48:37,000
That's the kind of antifinal, united course that ought to be coming from America and not this dentist dissonance of hate, of division, and instruction of human life.

817
01:48:37,000 --> 01:48:44,000
Thank you. I think we can put a line in the back.

